item.title: CVE-2020-10738|2024-08-04T11:14:14.722Z -- %5Bunknown%5D -- moodle
item.description: A flaw was found in Moodle versions 3.8 before 3.8.3, 3.7 before 3.7.6, 3.6 before 3.6.10, 3.5 before 3.5.12 and earlier unsupported versions. It was possible to create a SCORM package in such a way that when added to a course, it could be interacted with via web services in order to achieve remote code execution.
